# SQL directory
# SQL queries for data extraction and analysis

# Recommended files:
#   schema.sql                  — database schema definition
#   top_products.sql            — top products by revenue and units sold
#   revenue_trends.sql          — monthly/quarterly revenue aggregations
#   customer_lifetime_value.sql — CLV calculations per customer
#   rfm_query.sql               — Recency, Frequency, Monetary queries
#   cohort_query.sql            — cohort retention SQL
#   purchasing_patterns.sql     — basket analysis and repeat purchase rates
